data.text_input: I'm feeling relaxed and contemplative today. Looking for some chill indie folk music with acoustic guitars and thoughtful lyrics. I enjoy artists like Bon Iver, Fleet Foxes, and Sufjan Stevens. I want to avoid anything too energetic or loud like metal or EDM. I'll be reading and enjoying a cup of tea at home during the evening, so something that creates a peaceful atmosphere would be perfect.

I'm feeling nostalgic today and want to revisit the sound of 80s and 90s rock and pop. I love bands like Queen, Fleetwood Mac, and Michael Jackson. Would prefer to avoid current mainstream pop and trap music. I'll be driving on a road trip during the afternoon and want something I can sing along to that brings back memories.
